            "ratingValue": "2",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I just admitted my son this year in third class, Management and other things are good but i didn't find their study as up to mark.\nThey are using some module pattern for their primary classes they don't have subjects like other schools are doing.\nAnd their syllabus is very less as per today's competitive market.\nMy son has already covered many topics in his previous class and in little school and their module still don't cover those topics.\nSo as per me not good for study.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
